org.sbml.jsbml.ext

Interface ASTNodePlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Serializable, TreeNode, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractASTNodePlugin, MultiASTNodePlugin

    public interface ASTNodePlugin
extends TreeNodeWithChangeSupport
    Defines the methods necessary for an ASTNode or ASTNode2 Plugin. When a SBML level 3 is extending one of the mathML elements with additional attributes or child elements, a ASTNodePlugin is created to serve as a place holder for these new attributes or elements.
    Since:
    1.2
    Version:
    $Rev$
    Author:
    Nicolas Rodriguez
